  "texts": [
    "We prepared P. palmivora zoospores for the metabolite mobilization assay according to the following protocol.",
    "We prepared 125-mL Erlenmeyer flasks containing 25 mL V8 media.",
    "We placed two mycelial plugs in each flask and sealed them with foil and parafilm.",
    "In order to make sure pathogen cultures were kept in darkness, flasks were placed in a cardboard box in the incubator (27 °C) for 7 days.",
    "After 7 days, flasks were placed in 24-h light for 4 days, again at 27 °C."
  ],
